To use Tweet Me Tunes:

(1) Sign in to Twitter.
(2) Follow @tweetmetunes on Twitter.
(3) Go to http://tinyurl.com/tweetmetunes. If @tweetmetunes is following you, choose the direct message option from the drop-down menu. Otherwise, choose @reply.
(4) Enter the name of a track and/or artist in the search box and click "Tweet me tunes!"
(5) Click the "Tweet" button.
(6) You will receive a recommendation as an @reply.

You don't need to (nor will you be able to) execute the bot yourself.